<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recuperar Contraseña - Códigos de Oro</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-negro: #000000;
            --color-oro: #FFD700;
            --color-naranja: #FFA500;
            --color-gris-oscuro: #111111;
            --color-gris-fondo: #1a1a1a;
            --color-texto-claro: #f8e473;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--color-negro);
            color: var(--color-oro);
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-gris-oscuro) 0%, var(--color-negro) 100%);
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--color-negro);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-oro);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        p {
            color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.7);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .form-group {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: var(--color-gris-fondo);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.25);
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: var(--color-oro);
            outline: none;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        input:focus {
            border-color: var(--color-oro);
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: var(--color-oro);
            color: var(--color-negro);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: var(--color-naranja);
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .alert-error {
            background: rgba(200, 16, 46, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid #c8102e;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid #28a745;
            color: #71d08d;
        }

        .links {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--color-oro);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Recuperar Contraseña</h1>
        <p>Introduce tu correo electrónico y te enviaremos un enlace para restablecer tu contraseña.</p>

        @if(flashMessages.has('error'))
            <div class="alert alert-error">
                {{ flashMessages.get('error') }}
            </div>
        @endif

        @if(flashMessages.has('success'))
            <div class="alert alert-success">
                {{ flashMessages.get('success') }}
            </div>
        @endif

        <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST">
            {{ csrfField() }}
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Correo Electrónico</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="tu@email.com">
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Enviar Enlace</button>
        </form>

        <div class="links">
            <a href="/login"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Volver al Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
